PROGRAM-ID.	DESPRODCL.
AUTHOR.		GUZMAN Y CIA.

* Ejecuta un Comando DCL

ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
*====================

DATA DIVISION.
*=============
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
*-----------------------
COPY	FIOWSS	IN	DESTXT.
COPY	FRMWSS	IN	DESTXT.
COPY	'DESREG.CTL'	FROM	DICTIONARY
	REPLACING
	==CTL==		BY	==CTL EXTERNAL==.
01 DCL-VARI	EXTERNAL.
	03 DCL-CMN1				PIC X(60).
	03 DCL-CMN2				PIC X(60).
	03 DCL-IWRT				PIC 9(01).
		88 DCL-IWRT-NOT		VALUE 0.
		88 DCL-IWRT-YES		VALUE 1.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
*==================
MAIN SECTION.
*------------
INI-MAIN.
	IF NOT DCL-IWRT-YES
		MOVE 'NO FUE PROCESADO' TO FRM-MENS
		CALL 'DESPROFRM' USING FRM-MSG
		GO TO FIN-MAIN.
	MOVE DCL-CMN1 TO CTL.
*	MOVE SPACES TO CTL.
*	STRING '$ ' DCL-CMN1 DELIMITED BY CTL INTO CTL.
	CALL 'DESFIOCTL' USING FIO-PUT.
	CALL 'DESFIOCTL' USING FIO-CLO.
	CALL 'LIB$DO_COMMAND' USING BY DESCRIPTOR DCL-CMN2.
FIN-MAIN.
	EXIT PROGRAM.
